  "sections": {
    "Description": "The Alpha Firefly shoots projectiles in a direct line, similar to theTaurus Cannonweapon without push.",
    "Strategy": "The same strategy for the standardFireflycan be used to deal with the Alpha Firefly. They do have more health and deal more damage though, so blocking its projectile with your own Mechs is a lot more dangerous, likely fatal in the early-game on higher difficulties.\nThat said, if the Alpha Firefly goes early in the Attack Order, it can be pushed to force the projectile to take care of other enemies. Just like the standard Firefly, moving the Alpha or its target should still be done carefully, to avoid exposing Buildings to further danger."
  },
  "full_text": "Alpha Firefly\nDetails\nHealth\n5\nMove\n2\nSystems\nExpand\nEnhanced Thorax\n(\nEnemy\n)\nEffect\nLaunch a volatile mass of goo dealing 3 damage.\nAlpha Firefly\nis one of the Alpha\nVek\nfrom\nInto The Breach\n.\nDescription\n[\n]\nThe Alpha Firefly shoots projectiles in a direct line, similar to the\nTaurus Cannon\nweapon without push.\nStrategy\n[\n]\nThe same strategy for the standard\nFirefly\ncan be used to deal with the Alpha Firefly. They do have more health and deal more damage though, so blocking its projectile with your own Mechs is a lot more dangerous, likely fatal in the early-game on higher difficulties.\nThat said, if the Alpha Firefly goes early in the Attack Order, it can be pushed to force the projectile to take care of other enemies. Just like the standard Firefly, moving the Alpha or its target should still be done carefully, to avoid exposing Buildings to further danger.\nshow\nv\n·\nd\n·\ne\nVek\nVek\nBeetle\n•\nBlobber\n•\nBurrower\n•\nCentipede\n•\nCrab\n•\nDigger\n•\nFirefly\n•\nHornet\n•\nLeaper\n•\nScarab\n•\nScorpion\n•\nSpider\n•\nVolatile Vek\nVek (Advanced Edition)\nBouncer\n•\nGastropod\n•\nMosquito\n•\nMoth\n•\nPlasmodia\n•\nStarfish\n•\nTumblebug\nAlpha Vek\nAlpha Beetle\n•\nAlpha Blobber\n•\nAlpha Burrower\n•\nAlpha Centipede\n•\nAlpha Crab\n•\nAlpha Digger\n•\nAlpha Firefly\n•\nAlpha Hornet\n•\nAlpha Leaper\n•\nAlpha Scarab\n•\nAlpha Scorpion\n•\nAlpha Spider\nAlpha Vek (Advanced Edition)\nAlpha Bouncer\n•\nAlpha Gastropod\n•\nAlpha Mosquito\n•\nAlpha Moth\n•\nAlpha Plasmodia\n•\nAlpha Starfish\n•\nAlpha Tumblebug\nVek Psions\nBlast Psion\n•\nBlood Psion\n•\nShell Psion\n•\nSoldier Psion\nVek Psions (Advanced Edition)\nArachnid Psion\n•\nRaging Psion\n•\nSmoldering Psion\nVek Minions\nBlob\n•\nAlpha Blob\n•\nSpiderling Egg\n•\nSpiderling\n•\nAlpha Spiderling\nVek Minions (Advanced Edition)\nSpore\n•\nAlpha Spore\n•\nVicious Spore\n•\nBlob Leader\nVek Leaders\nBeetle Leader\n•\nFirefly Leader\n•\nHornet Leader\n•\nLarge Goo\n(\nMedium Goo\n) (\nSmall Goo\n) •\nPsion Abomination\n•\nScorpion Leader\n•\nSpider Leader\nVek Leaders (Advanced Edition)\nBlobber Leader\n•\nBouncer Leader\n•\nCentipede Leader\n•\nCrab Leader\n•\nGastropod Leader\n•\nMosquito Leader\n•\nPlasmodia Leader\n•\nScarab Leader\n•\nStarfish Leader\n•\nTumblebug Leader"
